<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-12205] nodetool tablestats sstable count missing.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-12205</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As a user, I have used  nodetool cfstats  since v2.1. The most useful line is the 1 like &apos;SSTable count: 12&apos;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;As a user, I want v3.7  nodetool tablestats  to continue showing SStable count. At the moment, SStable count is missing from the output.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Examples attached.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Cassandra 3.7&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
        <key id="12989515">CASSANDRA-12205</key>
            <summary>nodetool tablestats sstable count missing.</summary>
